                    <div class="article-byline open">
                        
                            <p class="article-byline-p">
                                <a href="http://www.climatecentral.org/what-we-do/people/brian-kahn"><img src="http://assets.climatecentral.org/images/made/BrianKahn_small_50_50_s_c1_c_t.jpg" alt="Brian Kahn" width="50" height="50" /></a>
                                By <a href="http://www.climatecentral.org/what-we-do/people/brian-kahn" rel="author">Brian Kahn</a>
